            <head>Sample Texts (Explanation)</head>

            <p>The sample texts are translations of the same
               <ref target="sample:msa_sample_01/Modern Standard Arabic">source text</ref>. They vary slightly with respect to regional
               differences. However, they are homogeneous enough to allow students to
               compare the numerous linguistic phenomena displayed in the texts.</p>

            <p>Sofar we provide sample texts for six locations: <list>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:baghdad_sample_01/Baghdad">Baghdad</ref>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:cairo_sample_01/Cairo">Cairo</ref>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:damascus_sample_01/Damascus">Damascus</ref>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:douz_sample_01/Douz">Douz</ref>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:urfa_sample_01/Şanlıurfa">Şanlıurfa</ref>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                     <ref target="sample:tunis_sample_01/Tunis">Tunis</ref>
                  </item>
               </list>
            </p>
